  <brief_title>Study of Sand Versus Wood Chip Surfaces on School Playgrounds to Minimize Injury in School Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>School Playground Surfacing - A Randomized Prospective Comparison of Injury Rates on Sand Versus Wood Chip Surfaces</official_title>
  <sponsors>
